#~ msgid ""
#~ "With the symmetric NUMA layout above "
#~ "(NUMA0 = 0..7, NUMA1 = 8..16), "
#~ "NPU0 stays within NUMA0, NPU2 stays "
#~ "within NUMA1, but NPU1 spans both "
#~ "NUMA0 (6,7) and NUMA1 (8..11). This "
#~ "is a direct consequence of global "
#~ "slicing over the ordered cpuset; the "
#~ "remainder distribution does not enforce "
#~ "NUMA boundaries."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "使用上述对称 NUMA 布局（NUMA0 = 0..7，NUMA1 = "
#~ "8..16），NPU0 保持在 NUMA0 内，NPU2 保持在 NUMA1"
#~ " 内，但 NPU1 跨越 NUMA0（6,7）和 NUMA1（8..11）。这是对有序"
#~ " cpuset 进行全局切分的直接结果；余数分配不强制 NUMA 边界。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If the cpuset numbering is interleaved"
#~ " across NUMA nodes (non‑symmetric layout),"
#~ " cross‑NUMA pools can happen even "
#~ "earlier. This is why symmetric NUMA "
#~ "layout is recommended for best locality."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "如果 cpuset 编号在 NUMA 节点之间交错（非对称布局），跨 NUMA"
#~ " 池可能会更早出现。这就是为什么推荐使用对称 NUMA 布局以获得最佳局部性。"

